Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That you want to learn to like yourself.}Rằng muốn trở nên yêu thích bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:12:02.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. But the harder I try on this project\Nright now, the more I feel lost.}Ừm, nhưng càng cố gắng thì tớ càng lạc lối.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I like it, though.}Tớ thì thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:11.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Y-you mean you like my art?}Hả? C-Cậu thích tranh của tớ á?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nah.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I like the way I am!}Thích bản thân tớ nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.13,Q26,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,57.6)}{\an7}{Storage Space}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Wow, this takes me back.}Hoài niệm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This was the first time, you know.}Cái này hình như là lúc bắt đầu nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That I fell behind you.}Lúc tớ thấy mình tụt lại sau cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Was it?}Thế á?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:28.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Aw, look at this. It's all skewed!}Cái gì thế này? Nhìn lệch hết tỉ lệ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{And the colors are weird. Way too uninhibited!}Màu sắc thì kì lạ nữa. Quá bất cẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{True.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But still...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's a nice painting, isn't it?}Là bức tranh rất đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh? These ones here...}Ủa? Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh. I guess these are ones I did.}À, là của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's been ages.}Hoài niệm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You really were so good.}Quả nhiên cậu cũng tuyệt nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, this was from third grade?!}Hồi tiểu học lớp 3 á?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:54.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! Can you believe it's the work of a\Nthird-grader?! It's so detailed.}Cái này mà của học sinh tiểu học á? Chi tiết quá vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:59.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I guess. But this really isn't anything, y'know?}Ừm, nhưng nó cũng chẳng có gì tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's how I am. I get the knack\Nof things faster than anybody.}Tớ lúc nào cũng nắm\N bắt mọi thứ nhanh hơn người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:07.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm the best at everything at the start,\Nand people treat me like a hero.}Lúc đầu luôn là người nhanh nhất, \Nai cũng xem tớ là anh hùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:13.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But then I get overtaken by the ones who\Npractice real hard or find passion in what they do.}Nhưng sau đó tớ bị vượt mặt bởi những người\N chăm chỉ và đam mê vào thứ họ thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's why...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I always quit before I get overtaken!}Tớ từ bỏ trước khi bị vượt mặt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{If I never lose, it's total victory for me!}Nếu không thua thì tức là tớ đã thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What? That's just sneaky.}Hả? Nghe bất công vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Look at this!}Nhìn nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:29.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Ooh, I remember this! It's my painting of you, Kiui.}A, là bức vẽ của tớ vẽ cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This game was all the rage at school, wasn't it?}Hồi xưa trò này từ rất nổi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It sure was. I wonder if that arcade's still there?}Ừm, không biết ở trung tâm trò chơi còn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're owning everyone here, Kiui.}Cậu áp đảo mọi người luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{How strong did you think I was back then?}Hồi đó cậu nghĩ tớ mạnh cỡ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You have to ask? You're invincible, Kiui!}Kẻ bất bại Kiui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Back then, maybe I was.}Đúng là hồi xưa thì thế thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey, I'm thinking of stopping by this arcade as well.}Tớ định ghé qua trung tâm trò chơi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.33,Q3,,0,0,0,,{So tired!}Mệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.00,Q3,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:02.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:03.92,Q3,,0,0,0,,{I'm hungry, too.}Đói quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:04.54,Q3,,0,0,0,,{I know.}Ừ ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.67,Q3,,0,0,0,,{I'm kinda craving pancakes.}Thèm bánh kếp ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:06.38,Q3,,0,0,0,,{Sounds great.}Nghe hay đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.00,Q3,,0,0,0,,{Right?}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Do you know them?}Người quen hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.08,Q3,,0,0,0,,{Let's go!}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nope, not in the slightest.}Không, người lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Then why...}Vậy tại sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Allow me to explain!}Để tớ giải thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{When you avoid school and shut yourself away at home,}Khi cậu nghỉ học và trốn trong nhà,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:22.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{the mere sight of a group clad in school uniforms is\Nenough to make you shy away in terror!}chỉ cần thấy một nhóm học sinh \Nmặc đồng phục cũng làm cậu khiếp sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, that's where you're supposed to laugh.}Đáng ra cậu phải cười chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Kiui...}Nè Kiui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:30.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You said you didn't get messages\Nfrom anyone, but is that really true?}Cậu nói không nhận được tin nhắn từ ai, có thật không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hamauchi and Mayumi?}Hamauchi và Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What? These are awful.}Gì thế này? Tồi tệ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well, I figure they never liked me to begin with.}Tớ cũng biết họ chẳng ưa gì mình từ đầu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{And I lied to everyone because\NI didn't want to let them down.}Và tớ nói dối mọi người vì không muốn họ thất vọng.
