Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:53.54,Q12,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.4,460.8)}{\an7}{Daichi Kitano\N}{\pos(371.2,511.2)}{\an7}{Student council's busier than I thought.\N}{\pos(499.2,561.6)}{\an7}{Wish I could go.}Muốn được đi quá www
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm just getting what I deserve.}Tớ phải trả giá cho những gì mình làm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{See, you can't change your past.}Cậu không thể thay đổi quá khứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:03.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I changed my looks and name and everything,\Nto start living a completely new life.}Tớ đã đổi tên, vẻ ngoài và mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:09.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But I get doxed once,\Nand it's straight back to square one.}Nhưng khi bị lộ ra thì tất cả quay trở lại như cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Allow me to explain!}Để tớ giải thích!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:20.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{K-Kiui Watase can edit videos and even come up\Nwith that amazing gig as JELEE's all-round super whiz!}Watase Kiui có thể chỉnh sửa video, \Nsáng tạo sân khấu trình diễn cho JELEE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.13,Q3,,0,0,0,,{Is she dancing?}Đang nhảy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:25.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Still to this day, in my eyes,\Nshe's an ever-shining superhero!}Đến tận ngày hôm nay, trong mắt tớ \Ncậu vẫn là một anh hùng tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:30.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What? That's so lame.}Gì thế? Nghe quê quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's not nice!}Này nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Thanks, though.}Cơ mà cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Okay! It's off to the arcade, then!}Được rồi, đi đến trung tâm game nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh? I can go alone-}Hả? Tớ có thể tự đi--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{No worries!}Đừng lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to run anymore.}Tớ không muốn bỏ chạy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:54.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{We used to come a lot on our days off with...\Nour friends from around here... huh?}Chúng ta đã từng đến đây hồi nhỏ với bạn bè...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I showed off and said I'd come along,}Xin lỗi, tuy vừa ra vẻ và đi cùng cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:00.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{but I'm so not ready for this, after all.}nhưng tớ chưa sẵn sàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Lemme run to the restroom.}Để vào nhà vệ sinh lấy tinh thần đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, sure.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh!}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's still here!}Nó vẫn còn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh hey! Mahiru?}Mahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hamauchi and Mayumi?!}Hamauchi và Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm here too!}Tớ cũng đến nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hamauchi and them are here. Let's split.}Hamauchi và mọi người cũng ở đây. Tạm thời chia ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:35.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Dude, Mahiru. I saw the thing about JELEE!}Mà tớ xem qua JELEE rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh... Thanks.}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Pretty impressive. I've been bragging\Nabout it to my entire class.}Đỉnh thật đó, tớ đã khoe với cả lớp luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{And hey, Watase's in JELEE too, right?}Và Watase cũng ở trong JELEE nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, Watase. That liar.}A Watase, con nhỏ dối trá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Why would you say that?!}Sao lại nói thế? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But it's true, right? She stopped\Ngoing to school, didn't she?}Nhưng sự thật mà? Cậu ta nghỉ học rồi còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:58.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{She used to be like, everyone's leader when\Nwe were kids, but people sure change, huh?}Ngày xưa lúc nào cũng đòi đứng đầu mọi người, \Nđúng là thời gian thay đổi mọi thứ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:04.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Kiui's still as cool as ever, okay?!}Kiui vẫn ngầu như mọi khi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:14.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, I remember now.\NYou used to always tag along with her, huh?}À nhớ rồi, hình như cậu hồi xưa toàn đi cùng cậu ta nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:18.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Come on, Kouzuki. You're famous now.}Thôi nào Kozuki, cậu đã nổi tiếng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:20.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Shouldn't you be growing out of that kind of thing?}Sao không trưởng thành lên đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This isn't about growing out of anything.}Trưởng thành cái gì chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I mean, she can't go to school? How lame is that?}Thì cậu ta còn chẳng thèm đi học mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, totally!}Phải đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're invincible, Kiui!}Kiui là tuyệt vời nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:38.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yo.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Wait, are you Watase?!}Hả? Watase?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What?! You look way different now.}Gì vậy? Hình tượng thay đổi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, Watase. Why'd you block us?}Cơ mà Watase, sao chặn tụi này thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What she said.}Đúng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{And here I thought we were friends. What a jerk move.}Cứ tưởng chúng ta là bạn bè đó, ác ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:06.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Those weren't messages you'd send to a friend...}Những tin nhắn đó mà là của bạn bè gửi à...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What? I can't hear you.}Hả? Nói gì không nghe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey. You guys!}Mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What was it again? Ryugasaki...?}Tên gì nhỉ? Ryugasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:14.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,Nox!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But that avatar acts like a guy, right?}Ảnh đại diện là con trai mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:22.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Are you like, one of those people\Nwho actually wants to be a guy?}Hay cậu thực sự muốn trở thành con trai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:23.50,Q3,,0,0,0,,{It's not... like that...}Không phải....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah! That "diversity" stuff?\NIt's like a trend these days, huh?}À à, lưỡng tính gì đó nhỉ? Gần đây nổi lên dữ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you just quit being weird\Nand live like a normal person?}Sao không dẹp cái bộ dạng kì lạ\N đó và trở lại bình thường đi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{...okay?}Toàn bộ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I said,}Tôi nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I never changed!}rằng mình chưa từng thay đổi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:44.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Not one bit, okay?!}Một chút nào cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{"Normal" people like you have no idea what it's like!}Bình thường mà các người nói là cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:51.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{To get mocked for just saying\Nyou love the things you love!}Bị chế nhạo vì yêu những thứ mình thích?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Your body keeps growing on its own,}Bắt buộc phải trưởng thành lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{and when you wear the clothes you like people stare!}và khi mặc quần áo mình thích\N thì bị người khác đánh giá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You don't know how that feels!}Các người thì biết gì về những cảm xúc đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But... still!}Nhưng mà tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I let the world get the better of me,}Đã chịu thua thế giới,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I couldn't even go to school and I hate myself for that!}từ bỏ trường học và ghét chính bản thân!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:11.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to love who I am as Kiui Watase again.}Tôi muốn được yêu quý bản thân mình lần nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I tried and tried but I couldn't!}Dù đã cố gắng nhưng không thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's why my looks, my voice,}Thế nên vẻ bề ngoài, giọng nói,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:22.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{my body, my personality,}cơ thể, tính cách,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:26.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{where I belong, my backstory...}nơi tôi thuộc về, câu chuyện của tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I created all that on my own so I could love myself!}Tôi đã tự mình tạo ra nó để có thể yêu bản thân!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{So don't deny me that!}Thế nên đừng có phủ định tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:34.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{The guy I created, the persona I love...}Nhân vật mà tôi tạo ra, tính cách mà tôi yêu mến...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I won't let anyone deny that identity!}Tôi không để ai phủ định nó đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:41.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm the unrivalled, invincible VTuber...}Tôi là Vtuber vô địch thiên hạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nox Ryugasaki!}Ryugasaki Nox!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:46.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You got a problem with that?!}Có vấn đề gì không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well... that's probably gonna get spread like wildfire.}Chà... có vẻ tin đồn sẽ lan rộng ra luôn quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Probably.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But still, you were so cool.}Nhưng cậu ngầu lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:10.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Really? I was being too real,\NI thought it was tacky as hell.}Thế hả? Nghĩ lại thì nó có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Cậu nói gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's what makes you awesome, Kiui.}Đó là điều khiến cậu tuyệt vời đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, maybe you're right.}Ừm, có lẽ cậu nói đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's goodbye, world.}Tạm biệt thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Cậu nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nono-tan, these lyrics...}Nono-tan, lời bài hát...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I figured it out.}Tớ quyết định rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Who I want to sing for.}Tớ muốn hát vì ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Can it, backseat gamer!}Gamer phía sau?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:49.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I play the way I wanna play!}Tôi chơi những gì mình thích!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:55.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's right, because this guy is\Nthe invincible VTuber Nox Ryugasaki!}Phải, vì tôi là Vtuber tuyệt vời nhất Ryugasaki Nox!
