Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:45.46,Q8,,0,0,0,,{Talking takes too long so I'll make it brief with a song}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:53.33,Q8,,0,0,0,,{Ever since that night I found you, the rhythm started accelerating}
